ZH: 这个月的水电账单是多少？
EN: How much is this month's utility bill?

ZH: 请把饭店的账单给我。
EN: Can you give me the bill for the restaurant?

ZH: 我能付现金结账吗？
EN: Can I pay the bill in cash?

ZH: 麻烦帮我查一下房租的账单。
EN: Can you please help me check the rent bill?

ZH: 最近手机账单比平时多了不少。
EN: Lately, the phone bill has been much higher than usual.

ZH: 需要每月提供交通费的账单。
EN: We need to provide the bill for transportation expenses every month.

ZH: 谁负责处理公司的账单？
EN: Who is in charge of handling the company's bills?

ZH: 这张账单上的金额有错误。
EN: There is an error in the amount on this bill.

ZH: 我们将通过邮件发送账单给客户。
EN: We will send the bills to the customers via email.

ZH: 您的医疗账单已经结清了。
EN: Your medical bill has been paid in full.

ZH: 您收到最新的信用卡账单了吗？
EN: Have you received the latest credit card statement?

ZH: 请将购物账单放在我的邮箱里。
EN: Please put the shopping bill in my mailbox.

ZH: 我们需要核查这个账单的项目。
EN: We need to verify the items on this bill.

ZH: 请注意，账单应在今天之前支付。
EN: Please note that the bill should be paid before today.

ZH: 这份账单已经过期了，需要重新开具。
EN: This bill has expired and needs to be reissued.

ZH: 我们将账单分发给了每个家庭成员。
EN: We distributed the bills to each family member.

ZH: 在结账时，饭店服务员忘记给我发账单。
EN: The restaurant waiter forgot to give me the bill when checking out.

ZH: 请在客户账单上签字确认。
EN: Please sign and confirm on the customer's bill.

ZH: 你可以通过手机应用支付电话账单。
EN: You can pay your phone bill through the mobile app.

ZH: 总经理审查了所有的报销账单。
EN: The general manager reviewed all the reimbursement bills.
